high_descs: Turn around, then go to the kitchen island on the left.
Pick up the knife that is between the two heads of lettuce.
Go around the kitchen island to the opposite side.
Slice the tomato on the right.
Turn right and take the knife to the microwave at the left of the fridge.
Put the knife in the microwave.
Turn around and return to where the tomatoes are on the kitchen island.
Take one slice from the tomato on the right.
Turn around and carry the tomato slice to the microwave.
Cook the tomato slice in the microwave and take it out.
Turn around and go to the green wastebasket to the left of the stove.
Throw the tomato slice in the wastebasket.
Turn around and walk across the room to the stove.
Take a left and walk to the center of the island on the left.
Pick up the sharp knife on the island that's between the two pieces of lettuce and go to the opposite side of the island.
Slice the tomato next to the plate.
Turn right and go to the microwave.
Open the microwave and put the sharp knife inside.
Turn around and walk back to the island where the sliced tomato is.
Pick up a slice of tomato.
Turn around and walk to the microwave on the right.
Put the tomato slice inside the microwave, use the microwave to heat up the tomato slice and take it back out.
Walk across the room to the trash bin next to the stove.
Put the heated tomato slice in the trash.
anns.task_desc: Put a slice of warm tomato into the trash bin.

high_descs: Move to the white island counter in the center of the kitchen.
Pick up the knife that is near the lettuce.
Move across the the other side of the counter by the tomatoes.
Use the knife to slice a tomato.
Move across the room to the microwave.
Place the knife inside the microwave.
Move across the room until you are at the counter with the slice tomato.
Pick up a slice of tomato off of the counter.
Move across the room to the microwave.
Place the tomato in the microwave. Turn the microwave on for a short time. Remove the cooked tomato from the microwave.
Move across the room to the green trash bin.
Discard the tomato into the trash bin.
anns.task_desc: Use a knife to slice a tomato, cook it in the microwave, & discarding the tomato in the trash bin.
